articles.description: Steph Curry has eclipsed many records in the NBA, won two MVPs and two rings. Oklahoma G Trae Young keeps piling up the stat sheet and continues to draw comparisons to Curry's game. The question is can Young keep it up?
articles.headline: Can Young follow in Curry's footsteps?

images.caption: Steph Curry has eclipsed many records in the NBA, won two MVPs and two rings. Oklahoma G Trae Young keeps piling up the stat sheet and continues to draw comparisons to Curry's game. The question is can Young keep it up?
images.name: Can Young follow in Curry's footsteps?

articles.description: Trae Young discusses not finding his rhythm anywhere on the court and facing Texas Tech's defense.
articles.headline: Young: 'Got to improve and I will'

articles.description: With senior captain Deshawn Freeman benched, star guard Corey Sanders had a game-high 30 points to lead Rutgers to a 67-58 overtime victory over Northwestern on Tuesday night at the RAC.
articles.headline: Sanders leads Rutgers to 67-58 OT win over Northwestern

articles.description: Tennessee hangs on to defeat South Carolina and improve to 9-4 in the conference.
articles.headline: No. 18 Vols get close win vs. Gamecocks 70-67

images.caption: Tennessee hangs on to defeat South Carolina and improve to 9-4 in the conference.

articles.description: Grant Williams scored 22 points and made a big basket in the closing seconds Tuesday as No. 18 Tennessee edged South Carolina 70-67 to hand the Gamecocks their sixth consecutive loss.
articles.headline: Williams helps No. 18 Tennessee outlast South Carolina 70-67
